ch/poem-uUdgeo6kWYZ5tkOilLUsJQ">Thôi Tông Văn thụ kê sách - 催宗文樹雞柵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-su%E1%BA%A5t-ph%E1%BB%A7-Tr%C3%ACnh-l%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BB%B1-ho%C3%A0n-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-0R6PFFKmcf-yrqdyojSIKQ">Tống suất phủ Trình lục sự hoàn hương - 送率府程錄事還鄉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-IV/poem-Pr5bZbe6uKNY9RWwhLqSnA">Vô đề (IV) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/author-1swHDuDfqhjQRVvirtpDBQ">Phạm Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-X/poem-0SZwNRYBxf54hpTE-EAEzA">Vô đề (X) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/author-1swHDuDfqhjQRVvirtpDBQ">Phạm Kỳ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
